Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFE100&\3a&HFF&\pos(408,984)}心澄如镜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(680,1017.667)} -> 正是所求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.18,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}因为想要守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.80,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}所以向着你呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:23.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}暗中宣战 献身歃血 以证逆命
